{"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericMoveSet\/continueTransaction"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:10NordicMesh18TransactionMessagePAAE08continueC0Sbvp::SYNTHESIZED::s:10NordicMesh14GenericMoveSetV","symbolKind":"property","title":"continueTransaction","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"continueTransaction"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","extendedModule":"NordicMesh"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericMoveSet"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"continueTransaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The messages within a transaction carry the cumulative values of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a field. In case one or more messages within a transaction are not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"received by the Server (e.g., as a result of radio collisions),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the next received message will make up for the lost messages,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"carrying cumulative values of the field."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A new transaction is started when this field is set to ","type":"text"},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or when the last message of the transaction was sent 6 or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"more seconds earlier.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This defaults to ","type":"text"},{"code":"false","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", which means that each new message will","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"receive a new transaction identifier (if not set explicitly).","type":"text"}]}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/genericmoveset\/continuetransaction"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Whether the message should start a new transaction.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/GenericMoveSet":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/genericmoveset","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"GenericMoveSet"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericMoveSet","title":"GenericMoveSet","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"GenericMoveSet"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[]},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh":{"abstract":[{"text":"Provision, configure and control Bluetooth mesh devices with nRF Mesh library.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"NordicMesh","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/GenericMoveSet/continueTransaction":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericMoveSet\/continueTransaction","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Whether the message should start a new transaction."}],"url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/genericmoveset\/continuetr